data.name: instructionsTextBox.Text
data.value:
Welcome to Blackjack!
You start with $1000 worth of betting money! Select chips to place bets, and select "DEAL" once bets have been placed to deal the initial 2 cards to you and the dealer. Use the "HIT" button to deal yourself another card, and select "STAND" to end your move and turn it over to the dealer. The dealer will complete their turn and then the winner will be displayed with corresponding rewards! Select "NEXT ROUND" to reset and place a new bet. Good luck!
